anyone to know he's home.

00:58.356 --> 01:01.268
Roger, please. I just want
20 minutes to myself, that's all.

01:01.489 --> 01:04.033
You know what a dog would do
at a time like this?

01:04.158 --> 01:05.343
He'd bark excitedly,

01:05.468 --> 01:07.650
alerting the family
that his master was home.

01:07.843 --> 01:08.953
Please, Roger, no.

01:09.078 --> 01:12.022
Of course, I suppose
if that dog were to get a treat...

01:12.147 --> 01:14.767
- What do you want? Anything.
- A carton of menthol lights,

01:14.892 --> 01:16.658
and I want look like Audrey Hepburn.

01:16.828 --> 01:18.318
I can give you all the cigarettes,

01:18.443 --> 01:20.635
but I can't make you look
like Audrey Hepburn.

01:24.323 --> 01:25.312
Dad's home!

01:25.437 --> 01:26.996
I haven't started the Parthenon.

01:27.121 --> 01:28.930
It's due tomorrow,
and I'm really tired.

01:29.131 --> 01:30.891
If we don't get
on the highway right now,

01:31.016 --> 01:32.975
