some time together later.

05:04.900 --> 05:06.200
Just you and me?

05:06.336 --> 05:08.323
I don't know, Francine.
I work all day,

05:08.448 --> 05:10.916
I spend time with the kids,
and I gotta sleep.

05:11.041 --> 05:13.450
- There's only so many hours in the day.
- I guess you're right.

05:13.575 --> 05:15.225
I'm just being selfish.

05:15.507 --> 05:16.523
Just a little.

05:19.299 --> 05:21.946
Dick, these pills saved my life.
I can't thank you enough.

05:22.185 --> 05:25.350
My pleasure. Make sure you never mention
the pills to your family.

05:25.475 --> 05:27.986
- They'll definitely want in.
- Oh, no way.

05:28.111 --> 05:30.482
This time is like a gift
from the heavens.

05:30.607 --> 05:34.333
