07:21.305 --> 07:22.617
It's completely dated!

07:22.742 --> 07:26.048
Pool boys and pizza guys
nailing lonely housewives?!

07:26.173 --> 07:28.296
Maybe I need to find
somebody else, Freddie.

07:28.421 --> 07:30.104
